### **Updating the `requirements.txt`**

Make sure you also include a **`requirements.txt`** file so that Streamlit Cloud (or any other environment) can easily install all dependencies. You can generate the `requirements.txt` by running:

```bash
pip freeze > requirements.txt
```

This file should include all the libraries needed to run your project, such as:
```txt
streamlit
matplotlib
requests
```

